      "title": "Susil to bring oil to Russia",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the Minister of Education Susil Premajayantha is scheduled to travel to Russia to discuss obtaining fuel from Russia.",
        "Former Sri Lankan Ambassador to Russia Saman Weerasinghe is also scheduled to accompany the Minister on this visit."
